        <Parent_String>sand [300014341], soil by composition or origin [300014331], soil [300014330], combination inorganic/organic material [300206579], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
